videos.headline: Belmont's Wells dishes the dime to Bartley for 2
videos.description: Destinee Wells shows off her skills with nice handles and smooth passes, and Madison Bartley finishes with the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Belmont's Wells dishes the dime to Bartley for 2) 2021/03/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wells drops in the reverse layup for Belmont
videos.description: Destinee Wells takes control as she drives through the lane and splits defenders to bank in the shot.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Wells drops in the reverse layup for Belmont) 2021/03/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gonzaga fights to stay in the game with O'Connor's 3
videos.description: With great ball movement from the Bulldogs, Abby O'Connor drains a triple to inch her team closer to Belmont.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Gonzaga fights to stay in the game with O'Connor's 3) 2021/03/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bartley's and-1 layup helps seal 12-seed Belmont's upset of Gonzaga
videos.description: Madison Bartley snatches the ball away down low and still makes the layup while drawing the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Bartley's and-1 layup helps seal 12-seed Belmont's upset of Gonzaga) 2021/3/22 ESHEET
